Global Automotive Radar Sensors Market Insights
Automotive Radar Sensors Market size was valued at USD 5.12 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 13.75 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 13.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Automotive Radar Sensors Market Overview
The automotive radar sensors market has witnessed significant growth and is projected to continue its upward trajectory in the coming years. The market was valued at approximately USD 6.5 billion in 2024 and is expected to reach around USD 12.2 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 11.3%. The market is driven by increasing demand for advanced driver assistance systems (ADAS) and the growing focus on vehicle safety and autonomous driving technologies. Radar sensors are crucial for providing real-time data, enabling features such as collision detection, adaptive cruise control, and lane-keeping assistance. The integration of radar sensors in vehicles offers a substantial reduction in accidents, making them a key component in the evolving automotive industry.

